snippet.title: Black Butterfly PV_En
snippet.description:
Intragames is pleased to announce the release of Psychedelica of the Black Butterfly Deluxe Bundle on STEAM®!

Psychedelica of the Black Butterfly Deluxe Bundle includes an Official Digital Art Book (English, Chinese and Korean), PC Wallpapers and an amazing digital OST consisting of 22 original sound tracks.
_______________________________________________________________________________
Psychedelica of the Black Butterfly Steam Page 

Visit(https://store.steampowered.com/app/967150/Psychedelica_of_the_Black_butterfly_DLC__Artbook_OST_Wallpaper/for more information and to keep up with all the latest news of Psychedelica of the Black Butterfly on STEAM®.
